Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就把之前的檸檬水加進去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最近暖和起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.23,0:00:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}馬上就要春天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.26,0:00:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}東鄉 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.71,0:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.01,0:00:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}事出突然 結城友奈要結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你你…你在說什麼啊 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你還只是國中生 而且對象呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是神樹大人
